        "title": "El Dorado Sets Sail",
        "text": "April 3rd, 1337. Clear. I, Kristoph Goldland, captain of the greatest ship in history—the El Dorado—am set to embark on her maiden voyage on this momentous day! One can scarcely imagine the splendor of the inaugural ceremony, but it was all worth it. This merchant vessel shall amass great wealth anew, and our first destination will be—the domain of the Landis! This affluent family will bring us our first great fortune.\n\n—Excerpt from the Captain's Log of the El Dorado",
